  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>([@@@@@@@@@] mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>En las últimas lecciones, hemos aprendido sobre fracciones equivalentes</q></p>
<p><q>¿Qué cosas importantes han aprendido sobre la equivalencia de fracciones?</q> (Fractions that are the same size are equivalent. Fractions at the same point on the number line are equivalent. Some fractions are equivalent to whole numbers, but some are not. Whole numbers can be written as fractions.)</p>

</subsubsection>



